---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';
---

<LandingLayout title="Privacy">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-12">Privacy</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600 space-y-12 leading-relaxed">
      
      <section>
        <p class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">Short version: your data is yours. We don’t sell it, and we don’t spy on you.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">What data we store</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">When you create an account, we store:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Your email address</li>
          <li>Your cycle data and logs (the information you enter into the app)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">This data exists only so the app can work and show you your history.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">What we do NOT do</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>We do not sell your data</li>
          <li>We do not show ads</li>
          <li>We do not share your personal data with third parties</li>
          <li>We do not track you across other websites</li>
          <li>We do not build an advertising profile about you</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Your control</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>You can delete your data.</li>
          <li>You can delete your account.</li>
          <li>When you do, your data is removed from our systems.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Why we collect data</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">Only to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Make the app work</li>
          <li>Sync your data</li>
          <li>Show your history across devices (if you use more than one)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">Nothing else.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="pt-8 border-t border-gray-100 mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions or want your data removed, contact us at:<br/>
          <a href="mailto:support@canihavesex.today" class="text-stone-900 underline underline-offset-4 decoration-stone-300 hover:decoration-stone-900">support@canihavesex.today</a>
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</LandingLayout>